column3: Come here. I need your help.
What are you trying to do?
I'm not nearly tall enough to jump around there, but I thought maybe you could. You look pretty tall.
Then why are you trying to get up there?
Great! Let me know when you're down.
Did you get up there yet?
Huh. That's disappointing. Thought there'd be, you know, something more interesting there.
Well, it must open something. Something secret. That's interesting, isn't it?
Huh. You're right! Let's go look for it.
Yeah. Be careful. You don't want to get trapped or anything.
